  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A new fast-paced FPS shooter FOR FREE!</h2>Enjoy a First Person shooter the way I wanted to see it!<br><br>The full release will contain:<br>- Various maps and gamemodes<br>- Unique weapons, weapon camos<br>- Scorestreaks<br>- Single-Player<br>- Co-op<br>- Progression system<br><br>This game is and will be completely micro-transaction free! You will never have to pay to get better equipment!<br>Weapons are accessible through cash earned during a match.<br><br>This whole game is being developed by me, a single person, so please understand that!<br>My goal is simply to make a fun free to play game.",
